text: Laura Fürst (born 23 April 1991) is a German wheelchair basketball player. She won a silver medal at the 2016 Summer Paralympics. She played at the 2011 Women's U25 Wheelchair Basketball World Championship, 2015 Women's U25 Wheelchair Basketball World Championship, 2014 Women's World Wheelchair Basketball Championship, and 2018 Wheelchair Basketball World Championship. == References == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Paralympic silver medalists for Germany Category:German wheelchair basketball players Category:Sportspeople from Munich
